msgid ""
"**Endpoints** for the API and Tunnel that match your network (VPC "
"``*.aliyun-inc.com`` or public ``*.aliyun.com``). See `Obtain endpoints "
"<https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/maxcompute/user-"
"guide/endpoints>`__."
msgstr ""
"与你的网络匹配的 API 和 Tunnel **Endpoint** （VPC ``*.aliyun-inc.com`` 或"
"公网 ``*.aliyun.com``）。参见 `获取 Endpoint <https://www.alibabacloud."
"com/help/en/maxcompute/user-guide/endpoints>`__。"

msgid ""
"**Paimon** Java/Python client libraries installed in the environment "
"where you run the write step (for example ``paimon_python_java``, "
"``paimon_python_api``, ``pyarrow``). Package names and install steps "
"follow your OpenLake onboarding guide."
msgstr ""
"在执行写入步骤的环境中安装 **Paimon** Java/Python 客户端库（例如 ``paimon"
"_python_java``、``paimon_python_api``、``pyarrow``）。包名和安装步骤请以"
"你的 OpenLake 接入指南为准。"

msgid ""
"**RAM or default credential chain** usable from notebooks (the sample "
"uses ``CredentialProviderAccount`` with ``DefaultCredentialsProvider``)."
msgstr ""
"Notebook 中可用的 **RAM 凭证或默认凭证链** （示例使用 ``"
"CredentialProviderAccount`` 和 ``DefaultCredentialsProvider``）。"

msgid ""
"A **DLF catalog** in the same region you configure, with **AccessKey** "
"pair or another supported credential for catalog APIs. See `Data Lake "
"Formation <https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/dlf/>`__."
msgstr ""
"在同一区域配置一个 **DLF catalog**，并准备用于 catalog API 的 **AccessKey"
"** 或其他受支持凭证。参见 `Data Lake Formation <https://www.alibabacloud."
"com/help/en/dlf/>`__。"

msgid ""
"A **MaxCompute project** with the **three-layer model** enabled (project "
"/ **schema** / object). See `Schemas "
"<https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/maxcompute/user-"
"guide/schemas-1>`__."
msgstr ""
"一个已启用 **三层模型** （project / **schema** / object）的 **MaxCompute "
"项目**。参见 `Schemas <https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/maxcompute/"
"user-guide/schemas-1>`__。"

msgid "Configuration placeholders"
msgstr "配置占位符"

msgid "End-to-end flow"
msgstr "端到端流程"

msgid ""
"For multimodal analytics, **unstructured data at scale** needs both "
"catalog metadata and a distributed runtime. **MaxCompute Object tables** "
"capture OSS object metadata automatically, while **MaxFrame** runs Python"
" transforms on that catalog. Combined with **OpenLake** (DLF + "
"**Paimon**), you can resize images in parallel and land curated bytes in "
"a lake table for retrieval, **AI Functions**, or downstream training."
msgstr ""
"在多模态分析场景中，**大规模非结构化数据** 既需要目录元数据，也需要分布式"
"运行时。**MaxCompute Object Table** 会自动采集 OSS 对象元数据，而 **"
"MaxFrame** 可以基于该目录运行 Python 转换。结合 **OpenLake** （DLF + **"
"Paimon**），你可以并行缩放图像，并将处理后的字节写入湖表，用于检索、**AI "
"Functions** 或下游训练。"

msgid "Further reading"
msgstr "延伸阅读"

msgid ""
"Install the **Paimon** Python bindings and **PyArrow** in the client "
"environment that runs this cell. The catalog uses the **``dlf-paimon``** "
"metastore type."
msgstr ""
"在运行该 cell 的客户端环境中安装 **Paimon** Python 绑定和 **PyArrow**。该"
" catalog 使用 **``dlf-paimon``** metastore 类型。"

msgid "MaxCompute"
msgstr ""

msgid "Multimodal image pipeline with OpenLake, Object Tables, and MaxFrame"
msgstr "使用 OpenLake、Object Table 和 MaxFrame 构建多模态图像流水线"

msgid "OpenLake: DLF + Paimon"
msgstr "OpenLake：DLF + Paimon"

msgid ""
"Optional **external project** name if you read the Paimon table through a"
" MaxCompute **external project** (``external_project_name`` in the "
"sample)."
msgstr ""
"如果通过 MaxCompute **外部项目** 读取 Paimon 表，可准备可选的 **external "
"project** 名称（示例中的 ``external_project_name``）。"

msgid ""
"Point ``LOCATION`` at the OSS prefix that stores images. **Refresh "
"metadata** before querying keys from MaxFrame."
msgstr ""
"将 ``LOCATION`` 指向存放图片的 OSS 前缀。在 MaxFrame 中查询 key 之前，"
"需要先 **刷新元数据**。"

msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前提条件"

msgid ""
"Session flags turn on **schema mode**, tune **object-table splitting** "
"for concurrency, and disable features that conflict with this lab-style "
"job."
msgstr ""
"Session 配置会开启 **schema 模式**，调整 **Object Table 切分** 以提升并发"
"，并关闭与该实验式作业冲突的功能。"

msgid "Step 1. Preview a public OSS object (optional)"
msgstr "步骤 1：预览公共 OSS 对象（可选）"

msgid "Step 2. Open a MaxFrame session"
msgstr "步骤 2：打开 MaxFrame Session"

msgid "Step 3. Create and refresh the object table"
msgstr "步骤 3：创建并刷新 Object Table"

msgid "Step 4. Inspect object metadata and one image payload"
msgstr "步骤 4：查看对象元数据和一张图片内容"

msgid "Step 5. Resize images in a MaxFrame UDF"
msgstr "步骤 5：在 MaxFrame UDF 中缩放图片"

msgid "Step 6. Run ``apply`` on MaxCompute"
msgstr "步骤 6：在 MaxCompute 上运行 ``apply``"

msgid "Step 7. Write the result to Paimon (DLF catalog)"
msgstr "步骤 7：将结果写入 Paimon（DLF catalog）"

msgid "Step 8. Read back from MaxCompute and visualize"
msgstr "步骤 8：从 MaxCompute 读回并可视化"

msgid "Step 9. Close the session"
msgstr "步骤 9：关闭 Session"

msgid ""
"The sample reads a single JPEG from a **public** demo prefix using "
"**anonymous** OSS auth. Replace ``bucket_name`` and ``object_key`` with "
"your own layout when you move to private data."
msgstr ""
"示例使用 OSS **匿名** 访问从一个 **公共** 演示前缀读取单张 JPEG。迁移到"
"私有数据时，请将 ``bucket_name`` 和 ``object_key`` 替换为你自己的目录结构"
"。"

msgid ""
"The sample reads through an **external project** bound to the lake "
"catalog. Adjust the fully qualified name to match your deployment."
msgstr ""
"示例通过绑定到 lake catalog 的 **external project** 读取数据。请根据你的"
"部署调整全限定名称。"

msgid ""
"This walkthrough uses a **public image folder** on OSS: metadata is "
"registered in an object table, a small **UDF** resizes each image to 150"
"×150 BMP, and results are written to **Paimon** through a DLF-backed "
"catalog."
msgstr ""
"本教程使用 OSS 上的一个 **公共图片目录**：先将元数据注册到 Object Table，"
"再通过一个小型 **UDF** 将每张图片缩放为 150×150 BMP，最后通过 DLF 支持的"
" catalog 将结果写入 **Paimon**。"

msgid ""
"Use the **Run this tutorial on DataWorks Notebook** button at the top for"
" the gallery entry that bundles the notebook and template assets."
msgstr ""
"可使用页面顶部的 **Run this tutorial on DataWorks Notebook** 按钮打开图库"
"条目，其中包含 Notebook 和模板资产。"

msgid ""
"`Schemas and namespace mode "
"<https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/maxcompute/user-guide/schemas-1>`__"
" for three-layer project layout."
msgstr ""
"三层项目结构请参见 `Schemas 与 namespace 模式 <https://www.alibabacloud."
"com/help/en/maxcompute/user-guide/schemas-1>`__。"

msgid ""
"`View and use custom images "
"<https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/maxcompute/user-guide/custom-"
"image>`__ if you extend the UDF with heavier dependencies."
msgstr ""
"如果需要为 UDF 扩展更重的依赖，请参见 `查看和使用自定义镜像 <https://www."
"alibabacloud.com/help/en/maxcompute/user-guide/custom-image>`__。"

msgid ""
"``@with_python_requirements`` ships **Pillow**, **pandas**, and "
"**cloudpickle** to workers."
msgstr ""
"``@with_python_requirements`` 会将 **Pillow**、**pandas** 和 **"
"cloudpickle** 分发到 worker。"

msgid ""
"``get_data_from_oss`` is a MaxCompute SQL helper that reads object bytes "
"for a given key; the notebook encodes them as **base64** so the Python "
"UDF can decode without mounting OSS inside the mapper."
msgstr ""
"``get_data_from_oss`` 是一个 MaxCompute SQL 辅助函数，用于按 key 读取对象"
"字节；Notebook 将其编码为 **base64**，这样 Python UDF 无需在 mapper 内"
"挂载 OSS 也能解码。"

